1.0.name: wordpress/vice-versa
1.0.description: Vice Versa vice versa vice-versa viceversa can easily convert WordPress Posts to Pages and Pages to Posts. You can also assign a Page or Post a parent or category(s) as you are converting from one to the other. Vice Versa is easy to install and use. No database tables are affected during installation and there are no additional settings required. Vice versa also has some premium modules to extend it's functionality. Premium modules include, Category to Category, Category to Post Type, and Post to Post Type conversions.
